==Dutch==

===Verb===
'''aangeven'''
# To [[hand]]; to [[pass]].
#: ''Kun je me de afstandsbediening aangeven?'' &mdash; Could you hand me the remote control?
# To [[indicate]]; to make [[clear]].
#: ''Hij heeft aangegeven waar het is.'' &mdash; He indicated where it is (to be found).
# To [[report]]; to [[notify]].
#: ''Iemand aangeven.'' &mdash; To report someone (to the authorities).
# To [[declare]].
#: ''Niets aan te geven.'' &mdash; Nothing to declare.

